text: NBC was an African pay television owned by NBC Universal International Networks. The channel was available on OSNtv. The channel launched on 24 September 2011 as Telemundo but was rebranded as NBC on 2 September 2014. The channel aired shows from the US NBC. The channel closed on 22 February 2023.
